dc_title_s: Storm Districts, San Joaquin County, California, 2015
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains the boundaries of storm districts in San Joaquin County, California as of July 2015. Storm districts are collectors of storm runoff to basins. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for San Joaquin County in California.This dataset is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
dc_publisher_s: San Joaquin County (Calif.). Community Development Department
dc_creator_sm: San Joaquin County (Calif.). Community Development Department
